### Test Approvals API - Phase 2 Day 5
### Approval Flow Testing

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
@documentId = 1
@workflowId = 1
@approvalId = 1

### 1. Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@acme.local",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### 2. Submit document for approval
POST {{baseUrl}}/approvals/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document_id": {{documentId}},
  "workflow_id": {{workflowId}}
}

### 3. Get my pending approvals
GET {{baseUrl}}/approvals/my-pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get document approval history
GET {{baseUrl}}/approvals/document/{{documentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get workflow instance for document
GET {{baseUrl}}/approvals/document/{{documentId}}/workflow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Approve document
POST {{baseUrl}}/approvals/{{approvalId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "Approved. Looks good!"
}

### 7. Reject document
POST {{baseUrl}}/approvals/{{approvalId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "Rejected. Please revise the document."
}

### 8. Request more information
POST {{baseUrl}}/approvals/{{approvalId}}/request-info
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "Please provide more details about section 3."
}

### ===== FULL WORKFLOW TEST =====

### Step 1: Create a test document
POST {{baseUrl}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_name": "test-approval-doc.pdf",
  "file_base64": "",
  "document_type_id": 1
}

### Step 2: Submit for approval (use document ID from step 1)
POST {{baseUrl}}/approvals/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document_id": 10,
  "workflow_id": 1
}

### Step 3: Check my pending approvals
GET {{baseUrl}}/approvals/my-pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Step 4: Approve (use approval ID from step 3)
POST {{baseUrl}}/approvals/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "Approved!"
}

### Step 5: Check workflow status
GET {{baseUrl}}/approvals/document/10/workflow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Summary:
# ✅ Submit for approval
# ✅ Get pending approvals
# ✅ Approve/Reject/Request Info
# ✅ Get approval history
# ✅ Get workflow instance
# ✅ Full workflow test
